---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Services – The IT Guys" description="Software development, mobile applications, web applications, custom software, and select technical consulting services.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
    <h1>Software development and practical technical solutions.</h1>
    <p class="lede">We create mobile apps, web applications, and custom software with a focus on reliability, clarity, and long-term maintainability.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="grid two">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Mobile Application Development</h3>
        <p>Design and development for iOS and Android applications, including product planning, app structure, user experience, and preparation for App Store and Google Play publishing.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Web Applications</h3>
        <p>Responsive web applications and product websites that are fast, accessible, and built to grow as the product evolves.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Custom Software</h3>
        <p>Purpose-built software for specific workflows, internal tools, prototypes, and technology problems that do not fit neatly into off-the-shelf solutions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Technical Consulting</h3>
        <p>Selective technical consulting informed by years of practical IT experience supporting businesses in British Columbia.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
